OL,6,FA campaign has been launched to rescue
OL,7,Fa one-of-a-kind aircraft with costs
OL,8,Fexpected to reach #60,000.
OL,10,FThe Blackburn Beverley is the only one
OL,11,Fof its model and is currently partly
OL,12,Fdismantled near Hull.
OL,14,FThe Solway Aviation Museum has bought
OL,15,Fthe plane but say transport and
OL,16,Frestoration costs could reach as much
OL,17,Fas #60,000.
