OL,3,CCampaign launched to rescue one-of-a-
OL,4,Ckind aircraft
OL,6,FDougie Kerr from the Solway Aviation
OL,7,FMuseum, said: "When it was flying with
OL,8,Fthe RAF when it started in 1956 it was
OL,9,Fthe largest aircraft that they had.
OL,11,F"It flew on until 1967 delivering
OL,12,Ftroops, bulldozers, everything you
OL,13,Fcould get in the back of it really.
OL,14,FYou could even get single decker
OL,15,Fbusses in the back. It took them all
OL,16,Faround the world in different
OL,17,Fconflicts including Vietnam, it went
OL,18,Feverywhere."
