OL,4,Ckind aircraft
OL,6,FThe average age of volunteers at the
OL,7,Fmuseum is around 70, but they say that
OL,8,Fthey're fighting fit and eager to be
OL,9,Fbusy with the new craft.
OL,11,FDougie Kerr added: "Back in 2020 when
OL,12,Fit was up for sale we put a bid in but
OL,13,Fwere out-bid by the chap who owned it
OL,14,Fup until we acquired it.
OL,16,F"He became stuck and couldn't move it,
OL,17,Fso we have almost come to the rescue
OL,18,Fnow."
