OL,3,CCampaign launched to rescue one-of-a-
OL,4,Ckind aircraft
OL,6,FThe Beverley will be the biggest plane
OL,7,Fthe museum has acquired, being
OL,8,Fslightly bigger than the Avro Vulcan
OL,9,FXJ823.
OL,11,FIt is an enormous job just to paint
OL,12,Fthe Vulcan as it can only be done
OL,13,Foutside when the weather isn't too wet
OL,14,For too hot with the last full repaint
OL,15,Fof the Vulcan taking 18 months.
OL,17,FDavid Kirkpatrick the Procurement
OL,18,FDirector at the museum said: "It has
OL,19,Fgot to be one of the biggest
OL,20,Fengineering jobs that we have ever
OL,21,Factually undertaken.
