OL,4,Ckind aircraft
OL,6,F"Our other large aircraft is the
OL,7,FVulcan which was actually flown in by
OL,8,Fthe RAF and parked, which was very
OL,9,Feasy. We will have to organise
OL,10,Ftransport to bring it up and it will
OL,11,Fbe several artic wagons.
OL,13,F"We will need cranes there and once we
OL,14,Fget it disassembled then it will be
OL,15,Floaded onto the wagons and
OL,16,Ftransported. We will have to negotiate
OL,17,Fwith the police for an escort. It will
OL,18,Fcome to the airport and then we will
OL,19,Frepeat the process in reverse and
OL,20,Fbuild it back up."
